A hook at `.cursor/hooks/track-feature-branch.sh` auto-reminds agents to do this on branch creation.

## Known Issues

- Gemini API keys get blocked if exposed in chat/git — never print or commit them
- Office/restricted networks may block PostgreSQL ports (5432/6543) to Supabase
- WebSocket chat not yet working (Redis TLS async issue with channels_redis) — uses REST fallback
- Frontend chat uses REST API (synchronous, not streaming) for now
